snippet.title: Goat Simulator Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
You can get it now at: 
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id868692227
GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.coffeestainstudios.goatsimulator
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/265930/

Goat Simulator is the latest in goat simulation technology, bringing next-gen goat simulation to YOU. You no longer have to fantasize about being a goat, your dreams have finally come true! WASD to write history.

Become a goat follower on Facebook! https://www.facebook.com/GoatSimulator

If you have any questions, tweet a sound a goat makes to https://twitter.com/Arminposts

Official wiki is here: http://goatsimulator.gamepedia.com/
